{"slug":"sirkuler-23-156-10496","reference":"Sirkuler_23_156","gazette":"Ministry of Commerce","title":"ANNOUNCEMENT REGARDING THE CUSTOMS PROCESS OF AID MATERIALS SENT FROM ABROAD","date":"07 Şubat 2023","bodyHtml":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">ANNOUNCEMENT REGARDING THE CUSTOMS PROCESS OF AID MATERIALS SENT FROM ABROAD</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">It is possible to import basic necessities and other goods sent from abroad to be distributed free of charge to the people affected by the earthquake or put into their use, without being subject to customs duties and trade policy measures if they are sent to the;<o></o></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Public institutions and organizations<o></o></span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Associations working for public benefit<o></o></span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Foundations granted tax exemption by the President</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">In order to ensure regular coordination by the relevant Ministries, the goods arriving within this scope must be sent to any of the institutions/organizations listed below:<o></o></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">AFAD<o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Ankara Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Ankara Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)</i><o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Şanlıurfa Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Şanlıurfa Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)<o></o></i></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Kahramanmaraş Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Kahramanmaraş Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)</i><o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Adıyaman Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Adıyaman Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)</i><o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Adana Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Adana Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)<o></o></i></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Hatay Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Hatay Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)</i><o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Diyarbakir Social Assistance and Solidarity Foundation <i>(Diyarbakır Sosyal Yardımlaşma ve Dayanışma Vakfı)<o></o></i></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">It is sufficient to submit the;<o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">Transport documents if any<o></o></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">List of items (according to the example below)<o></o></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">to the customs office from which they came to carry out the customs procedures for the goods in question.<o></o></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" xss=\"removed\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" xss=\"removed\">LIST OF ITEMS SENT TO THE PEOPLE AFFECTED IN THE EVENT OF THE CRISIS<o></o></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"664\" xss